===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

# the [[Jew]]ish [[religion|religious]] practice that specifies which [[food]] is fit to [[eat]] and how it is to be [[prepare]]d.

====Translations====
*Finnish: [[kosher]]
*Hebrew: [[כשר]]

===Adjective===
{{en-adj|-}}

# {{italbrac|of food}} prepared in accordance with Jewish religious practices.
# {{italbrac|generally}} in accordance with standards or usual practices, 
:i.e ''"Is what I have done '''kosher''' with Mr Smith?"''  

